page.title: 14A TYPICAL DAY IN DANE END
page.content: {A DAY IN MY LIFE:}Every morning I get up at 6:45 I have a wash and get dressed. Then I go down stairs to see my puppy called Bennett I let him out into the garden and make his breakfast. I also give my cat some munchies. They are like tiny flavoured biscuits. Then I make my own breakfast and either listen to the radio or watch the tv. My Mum and Dad get up and come down stairs and have their breakfast and Mummy makes our packed lunches. Sophie, Marcus and Luke have their breakfast as well. We say good-bye to Mum and Luke and Daddy takes us to school. At school our subjects are English, Mathematics, Art and Craft, Geography, French, Science, Handwriting and Reading. Our lunch break is at 12noon.We go home at 3pm.After school I usually play with my friends and go to bed at 8.30 pm.
